quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  4,66,"And had We prescribed unto them: slay yourselves or go forth from your dwellings, they had not done it, save a few of them. And did they do that which they are exhorted to do, it would be for them better and more strengthening"
  4,67,And then We would surely have vouchsafed unto them from Our presence a mighty hire
  4,68,And We would surely have guided them on the right path
  4,69,"And whosoever obeyeth Allah and the apostle, then those shall be with them whom Allah hath blessed --from among the prophets, the saints, the martyrs, and the righteous. Excellent are these as a company"
  4,70,"That is the grace from Allah, and sufficeth Allah as Knower"
  4,71,O Ye who believe! take your precaution then sally forth in detachment or sally forth all together
  4,72,"And verily there Is among you he who laggeth behind, and if an ill befalleth you, he saith: surely Allah hath bestowed favour on me in that I was not Present with them"
  4,73,"And if there betideth you grace from Allah, then, as though there had been no tenderness between you and him, he saith: would that I had been with them! then I would have achieved a mighty achievement"
  4,74,"Let them wherefore fight in the way of Allah those who have purchased the life of this world for the Hereafter: And whosoever fighteth in the way of Allah, and is then slain or overcometh, We shall vouchsafe unto him a mighty hire"